cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.SY 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) as it proposes an algorithm for multi-modal imitation learning. It also involves supervised learning techniques (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV) as it deals with road scene simulations. Additionally, it relates to robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY) as it aims to imitate expert autonomous driving systems over long time horizons.
